quran[15]{c,v,t}:
  20,99,"Ko wano nii Men polloranay maa immorde e kumpital ko feƴƴunoo kon, gooŋɗii Men ngaddanii ma immorde ka Amen jaŋta."
  20,100,"Mo ɗuurike e mayre pellet, o ronndoto Ñande Darngal teddeele [bakkaatu]."
  20,101,"Ko o luttinteeɗo e ndeer majje, bonanii ɓe donngal Ñande Darngal."
  20,102,"Ñaande wuttoytee ka alaadu Min mooɓa bonɓe ɓen nden Ñalnde ko mbuliiɓe [gite]."
  20,103,"Heɓe sowndondira hakkunde maɓɓe [ɓe mbi'a] on ñiiɓaani si wonaa [balɗe] sappo."
  20,104,"Ko Minen ngoni Annduɓe ko ɓe wowlata kon, tuma nde koohooɓe maɓɓe e laawol wi'ata: "On ñiiɓaani si wonaa ñallal"."
  20,105,"Heɓe lanndaade ma fii pelle ɗen, maaku: "Joomi am ƴaroto ɗe e ƴaragol"."
  20,106,"O acca [leydi] ndi ko ndi boowal ɓowrungal."
  20,107,"A yi'ataa e mayri ooñannde wonaa tintiire.(naɗde)."
  20,108,"Ko nden Ñande ɓe njokkata noddoowo on ko aldaa e celugol mo,, hitooji ɗi yankinanoo Hinnorante On hara a nanataa si wnaa ñu'umbaangol."
  20,109,"Nden Ñande tefoore nden nafataa, si wonaa on mo Hinnorante On sakkiti ɗum O weltori konngol makko."
  20,110,"Homo Anndi ko woni ko yeeso maɓɓe e ɓaawo maɓɓe ɓe kuɓindortaa ɗum ganndal."
  20,111,"Je'ece ɗen yankinanii guruɗo Dartiiɗo On, gooŋɗii sooyii on donndiiɗo tooñe."
  20,112,"On mo ngolli immorde e moƴƴi ɗin hara ko o gooŋɗinɗo o hulaa tooñe wonaa uytaneede kadi."
  20,113,"Ko nii Min Telliniri nde Alqur'aanaare Aarabuure Men fensiti kadi e nder mayre immorde e kammbaaji ɗin mbela-jo'o kamɓe ɓe kulat maa nde fuɗɗanoo ɓe waaju."